The evidence with the title 'Understanding how raising the federal minimum wage affects ... ' says Mar 12, 2014  ... According to economic estimates , raising the minimum wage to $10.10 an hour will reduce the poverty rate for non - elderly Americans to 15.8 percent ... Earning the current federal minimum wage , a minimum - wage earner working 40 hours a week every week of the year would earn $15,080 over the year. 
